{"tid":1440814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理優十八區新戰線]想集思廣益 用民生議題反制黑警濫暴","createTime":"2019-08-10T13:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:38:45.000Z","uid":288401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f0885da3892f9221897feee998385f4f8b6e84","tid":1440814,"uid":288401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"[和理優十八區新戰線]<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，相信大家連日來都見到馬鞍山、沙田TG放題，影響到唔少居民、老人、小朋友甚至乎動物同浪浪，確實有唔少街坊藍轉黃，幫口圍差佬，但無奈佢地wfc，同永遠覺得我地只係小眾，要俾到壓力政府同警察，需要有實質數據，以及有牙力既團體代我地將議題帶入公眾。<br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以收集聯署，以「居民自發 停止以暴制亂 粗暴對待居民及濫發催淚神經毒氣 」，將收集到既聯署分類交俾所屬管理公司，再透過佢地向政府同警察施壓，可以結合當區區議員或社區團體去做。<br />\n<br />\n我p牌，社運經驗少，放上黎集思廣益，<br />\n知道聯署簽左十幾廿萬個，但似乎無人將聯署成功帶入議題，所以諗左呢個方法，可能無咩用，睇下可唔可以幫到前線食少d TG，唔掂既再諗，掂既就試下大家巴絲分區做！<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cd4569dfc4f7be457d4733aa6c52bfd842dafced","tid":1440814,"uid":288401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"連豬豬十連推po是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eab98f79f2539c40432875efbcd390e98face04","tid":1440814,"uid":288401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd45ff4b3eece30636072a7d5d5fb9430a4d8c3f","tid":1440814,"uid":288401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52649238b1f3f53117dcb996007cd8cbf259d3a","tid":1440814,"uid":288401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 